OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of Neal's Yard cheese
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the theft of
OL,7,Fmore than 22 tonnes of cheese from a
OL,8,FLondon-based artisan cheese retailer
OL,9,Fand distributor have arrested a 63-
OL,10,Fyear-old man on suspicion of fraud and
OL,11,Fhandling stolen goods.
OL,13,FNeal's Yard, a British, London-based,
OL,14,Fartisan cheese retailer and
OL,15,Fdistributor, said it delivered more
OL,16,Fthan 950 wheels of cheddar to the
OL,17,Falleged fraudster posing as a
OL,18,Fwholesale distributor for a major
OL,19,FFrench retailer before realising what
OL,20,Fhad happened.
