OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police spokesman said:
OL,7,F"On Monday October 21, police received
OL,8,Fa report of the theft of a large
OL,9,Fquantity of cheese from a manufacturer
OL,10,Fbased in Southwark.
OL,12,F"Investigating officers have since
OL,13,Farrested a 63-year-old man on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of fraud by false
OL,15,Frepresentation and handling Stolen
OL,16,FGoods.
