OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of Neal's Yard cheese
OL,6,F"The man was taken to a south London
OL,7,Fpolice station where he was
OL,8,Fquestioned. He has since been bailed
OL,9,Fpending further inquiries. Inquiries
OL,10,Fremain ongoing."
OL,12,FNeal's Yard said it still paid Hafod,
OL,13,FWestcombe and Pitchfork, the producers
OL,14,Fof the cheese, so they would not have
OL,15,Fto bear the cost "despite the
OL,16,Fsignificant financial blow".
