OL,6,FThe company have called out to
OL,7,Fcheesemongers around the world to
OL,8,Fcontact them if they suspect they have
OL,9,Fbeen offered or sold the stolen
OL,10,Fcheese, particularly clothbound
OL,11,Fcheddars in a 10kg or 24kg format with
OL,12,Fthe tags detached.
OL,14,FCelebrity chef Jamie Oliver also
OL,15,Fappealed to his followers on social
OL,16,Fmedia to be alert for "lorryloads of
OL,17,Fposh cheese" being sold "for cheap".
