OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of Neal's Yard cheese
OL,6,FHe told his 10.5 million followers:
OL,7,F"There has been a great cheese
OL,8,Frobbery. Some of the best cheddar
OL,9,Fcheese in the world has been stolen."
OL,11,FTom Calver, director of Westcombe
OL,12,FDairy in Westcombe, Somerset, produced
OL,13,Fsome of the stolen cheese and said he
OL,14,Fwas "hugely distressed" when he heard
OL,15,Fthe news.
OL,17,FMr Calver, 42, said: "I was really
OL,18,Fconcerned about what it was and the
OL,19,Fimplications of it.
