OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of Neal's Yard cheese
OL,6,F"Neal's Yard have been fantastic. We
OL,7,Fare just trying to support them as
OL,8,Fmuch as possible by encouraging people
OL,9,Fto shop with them. It is a huge, very
OL,10,Fdifficult loss.
OL,12,F"What it does show, which I am amazed
OL,13,Fabout, is the value people put on
OL,14,Fthese amazing artisan foods."
OL,16,FMr Calver's Westcombe Cheddar is aged
OL,17,Ffor 12 to 18 months and he said the
OL,18,Fstolen cheese was produced 15 months
OL,19,Fago.
