OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of Neal's Yard cheese
OL,6,FHe said: "What worries me is the trust
OL,7,Felement in things. At the end of the
OL,8,Fday, what we need to have is more
OL,9,Ftrust in the food supply system,
OL,10,Frather than less of it. I hope more
OL,11,Fpeople will want to know where their
OL,12,Ffood comes from."
OL,14,FNeal's Yard said it was working with
OL,15,Fpolice to identify the perpetrators.
